{"tid":2011473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 連登需唔需要成立一支連衛兵？","createTime":"2020-05-11T04:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T10:18:26.000Z","uid":29381,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3be49aed3df769e2962dc90db309fe46514d097","tid":2011473,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>正皮=支持 負皮=反對</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n非官方精英路線 大既有10+連登仔就得<br />\n1) 抗衡5毛 (帶風向/引戰/歪理/分化)<br />\n2) 推動全民學習 (集中推1~3個學術POST)<br />\n3) 研判連登風氣<br />\n <br />\n成立連衛兵 係希望有系統性地處理上述幾點<br />\n同埋亦想組織有識之士一齊參與網絡鬥爭 <br />\n<br />\n暫時係以上3點 有餘力先做其他野 大家點睇？"},{"pid":"41accb57d053c4661d9143b557cd44dbd95d9a7e","tid":2011473,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e7c117978e5a81069077bb797ff81df671de50","tid":2011473,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"獨立思考 完"},{"pid":"5ca5b963f519eb9fb511475315fb1769c880f540","tid":2011473,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e7c117978e5a81069077bb797ff81df671de50","tid":2011473,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"獨立思考 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"獨立思考左差唔多一年 成績點?<br />\n一盤散沙妄想同全世界最大既黑社會鬥?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb57bcc0b18450e9882b1888a879f6c00730153f","tid":2011473,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"軍隊點解要分軍、師、旅、團、營、連、排、伍咁撚多階級？點解唔獨立作戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe1bdb0aa947ad575a7ee1a1bc13fbb4dcde2f9","tid":2011473,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img